column2: "There are a lot of Darkers. I wonder if they're responding to his presence?"
"Seems like it would cause a huge problem for the Dragonkin."
"I wonder if that's why I was forced to negotiate before..."
"He knew it would turn out like this, which is why he put us in this situation."
"Who are we going to meet here?"
"Don't worry about that. Once you see, you'll understand. But, that's not the answer you want."
"I'll give you a hint - it's a little brat."
"He's very cocky. Crammed into a complaining, high-grade runt."
"Even though he doesn't try to do anything himself, he continuously critiques everyone."
"Just talking about him has really started to piss me off."
"Chit-chat aside, we should hurry up and get going."
